Test space for developers. All modules are activated. The header and the banner images don't work by default, they need to be reuploaded (edit space). The space is set by default to "private". There are three users: admin, testmod and testuser.
Example of proposal inside a set

This is a proposal inside a proposal set, this feature is for wrapping up proposals and discuss a theme relates with a debate, for example, using a fdebate to identify problems and using a set tied to that debate to propose solutions to the identified problems.
Sometimes you don't need to tie proposals to a debate, so you just can make proposals related to whatever you want. In this case the proposal also has tags and geographic info
